# GrammarHelper Finalization Plan

This plan outlines the steps necessary to transform the current foundational codebase into the fully realized **Grammar Expert / GrammarHelper** application as defined in the **Group 20-GE Proposal**, **Ultimate Concept Document**, and **Architecture Blueprint**. 

The application skeleton (MVVM folders, Gemini API connection, Room DAOs, MPAndroidChart UI, and the Floating Bubble overlay) is remarkably accurate to the spec. This phase focuses entirely on **connecting the data layer to the UI** and **polishing the interactive flows** to achieve the "Educational AI Tutor" goal.

